Age
	DESC:A Curseborn's body does not age naturally, and they may lice as long as their bodies persist. Those that are made well may last for centuries.
Alignment
	DESC:Curseborn often retain the alignment from their first life. Their morals persist, even if they cannot recall why.
Size
	DESC:Curseborn generally stand between 5 and 6 feet tall, those some hulking amalgamations may reach as high as 8. Your size is medium.
Speed
	DESC:Your base walking speed is 30 feet.
Darkvision
	DESC:Regardless of their capability before, your eyes now pierce the darkness. You can see in dim light within 60 feet of you as if it were bright light, and in darkness as it were dim light. You can't discern color in darkness, only shades of gray.
Not Again
	DESC:When reduced to 0 hit points and not killed outright, you must succeed five death saving throws to become stable, and fail five death saving throws to die.
Languages
	DESC:You can speak, read, and write Common and one extra language of your choice, typically recalled from your previous life or imbued by your creator.
Subrace
	DESC:Curseborn fall into one of two broad categories. The Occult are given life by enchantments that bind their forms together, while Amalgamations are composed of viable parts from cadavers, combined and given life.

